tures a robust weapon crafting and customization system. Let\u2019s be honest: You won\u2019t survive the apocalypse using a mere baseball bat or machete. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/once-human-acid-gunpowder-ammo-polluted-1851597504\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 884188, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/once-human-acid-gunpowder-ammo-polluted-1851597504", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b220a35a4f18dcf56fd57506d123e77a.jpg", "title": "The Best Ways To Farm Acid In Once Human", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T20:00:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/dc17b1efd48d12ed958f095d2f83022c.jpg\" /><p>Today\u2019s most popular and best-selling games often include expensive first-party exclusives, big multiplayer hits, and aging titles like GTA V that stick around years after launch. But that wasn\u2019t the case 20 years ago, as seen in newly published sales data.<br /></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/best-selling-games-2024-2004-ncaa-spider-man-shrek-ps2-1851597357\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 883785, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/best-selling-games-2024-2004-ncaa-spider-man-shrek-ps2-1851597357", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/dc17b1efd48d12ed958f095d2f83022c.jpg", "title": "Here's How Today's Best-Selling Games Compare To Those From 20 Years Ago", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T19:20:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/508c8289b56bc51021dbcf37398a409a.jpg\" /><p>After months of critical and public acclaim, Amazon\u2019s <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/fallout-show-amazon-review-1851400505\">Fallout series</a> can now add \u201cEmmy nominated\u201d to its list of superlatives. The <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/mediocre-video-game-show-bandersnatch-wins-emmy-1838365133\">annual television awards</a> show just released the <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/2024\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">full list of this year\u2019s nominees</a>, and while the adaptation of the<a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/best-fallout-games-3-4-5-76-bethesda-rpg-new-vegas-611408965\"> post-apocalyptic RPG games</a> didn\u2019", "id": 883786, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/2024-emmy-nominations-fallout-walton-goggins-shogun-1851597281", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/508c8289b56bc51021dbcf37398a409a.jpg", "title": "Amazon's Fallout Series And Star Walton Goggins Score Emmy Nominations", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T19:00:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/2b4a2ef86879849a31b8a287d510f559.jpg\" /><p>Even when its initial launch left some players feeling underwhelmed and disappointed, no one could deny No Man\u2019s Sky was an absolutely gorgeous game. Nearly eight years later, the sci-fi exploration sim looks more stunning than ever in a <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/no-man-sky-patch-5-0-free-helldivers-mechs-1851596276\">comprehensive new 5.0 patch</a> that adds a bunch of things and changes a ton of\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/no-man-sky-worlds-5-0-patch-art-graphics-ps5-sale-1851596991\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 883474, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/no-man-sky-worlds-5-0-patch-art-graphics-ps5-sale-1851596991", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/2b4a2ef86879849a31b8a287d510f559.jpg", "title": "19 Incredible No Man's Sky Views That Will Make You Want To Jump Back In", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T18:00:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b6e59f0837009a3541df14622350c3eb.jpg\" /><p>There\u2019s a hell of a lot of harassment going on in gaming. If there\u2019s one thing Kotaku would like to see, it would be big-name publishers speaking up about it, and taking a stand against it, instead of capitulating to it or tacitly endorsing it through silence. Meanwhile, there\u2019s Sega\u2019s approach <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.eurogamer.net/sega-sues-social-media-user-for-excessive-slanderous-and-insulting-comments-against-employee\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">spotted by Eurogamer</a>,\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/sega-sues-online-troll-defamation-lawsuit-1851596985\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 883028, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/sega-sues-online-troll-defamation-lawsuit-1851596985", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b6e59f0837009a3541df14622350c3eb.jpg", "title": "Sega Sues Online Troll Who Harassed Its Staff, And Wins", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T17:50:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/e089d18cd3d8627994ee28ab69b9776a.jpg\" /><p>Last year, a growing trend saw AAA video game publishers offering early access to new games if you pre-ordered a pricey special edition version. I worried then that if some publishers were successful in locking games behind a ransom fee, many others would do the same in the future. And here we are, in 2024, and most\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/paid-early-access-pre-order-madden-star-wars-outlaws-1851596675\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 883029, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/paid-early-access-pre-order-madden-star-wars-outlaws-1851596675", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/e089d18cd3d8627994ee28ab69b9776a.jpg", "title": "Greedy Publishers Have Won And Normalized Paying To Play Early", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T17:15:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/1918f6dbded56c349bfc92803edf6213.jpg\" /><p>The Perfumer\u2019s Talisman that can be found in Elden Ring\u2019s Altus Plateau region in the base game. If you\u2019re running any build that makes use of Perfume weapons, such as <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-lightning-perfumer-build-1851589470\">the Lightning Perfumer Build for Shadow of the Erdtree</a>, this accessory should be at the very top of your list, as the damage buff it provides is\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-perfumer-build-talisman-location-1851596833\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 883030, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-perfumer-build-talisman-location-1851596833", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/1918f6dbded56c349bfc92803edf6213.jpg", "title": "Amplify Your Perfume Damage In Shadow Of The Erdtree With This Talisman", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T17:07:51+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b1b0f58138482576a3fd830708cc33c1.jpg\" /><p>Though Supergiant Games largely has its head down as it works on Hades 2\u2019s first major update coming later this year, the <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/hades-2-early-access-review-1851496575\">already phenomenal sequel</a> is still getting <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/hades-2-patch-notes-buff-chronos-steam-early-access-1851519615\">patched throughout early access</a>. Its <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1145350?emclan=103582791472836561&amp;emgid=6231376270663101766\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">latest update</a> isn\u2019t focused on any one thing, but aims to fix a lot of issues that have been observed since the\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/hades-fourth-patch-fi", "id": 883031, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/hades-fourth-patch-fixes-balance-changes-1851596804", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b1b0f58138482576a3fd830708cc33c1.jpg", "title": "Hades 2\u2019s Fourth Patch Nerfs Some Overpowered Builds Ahead Of First Major Update", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T16:37:18+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/77fb63dc22be57c2702de1f6313e6de2.jpg\" /><p>When you first jump into loot shooter The First Descendant, you\u2019ll think, \u201cWow, this is easy!\u201d And for the most part, you\u2019d be right. The gameplay is straightforward, character movement and power feel wonderful, and despite the <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/the-first-descendant-is-caliber-worth-spending-real-mo-1851595265\">numerous currencies</a> and menus, everything is clear with some guidance. But then you hit the\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/the-first-descendant-kuiper-shard-farming-location-1851596736\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 882489, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/the-first-descendant-kuiper-shard-farming-location-1851596736", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/77fb63dc22be57c2702de1f6313e6de2.jpg", "title": "How And Why You Should Be Farming Kuiper Shards In The First Descendant", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T16:25:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b34a927ec051c63107acae6021e29a71.jpg\" /><p>As a New Yorker in my late twenties, it\u2019s only a matter of time until I get into birding. <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/flock--2\">Flock</a> might be the thing that finally makes me take the plunge into the hobby. The new shepherding/creature collecting game from developer Hollow Ponds is full of color and life, inviting you to explore its vibrant world and sate\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/flock-impressions-playstation-hohokum-cozy-game-1851596671\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 882490, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/flock-impressions-playstation-hohokum-cozy-game-1851596671", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b34a927ec051c63107acae6021e29a71.jpg", "title": "Flock Is This Summer's Best Chillfest", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T15:57:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/04d7b80e41f252b41fce8abf7234cdef.jpg\" /><p>Palworld has seen updates here and there since its launch earlier this year, but its biggest came on June 27, 2024 with the Sakurajima update. In addition to a slew of new endgame content and updated mechanics, the focal point is the eponymous island that makes up the game\u2019s latest region. But what should you do when\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/palworld-sakurajima-pals-catch-selyne-oil-1851596620\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 882012, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/palworld-sakurajima-pals-catch-selyne-oil-1851596620", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/04d7b80e41f252b41fce8abf7234cdef.jpg", "title": "8 Essential Things To Do In Palworld\u2019s Sakurajima Region", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T14:15:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/14ed0ec3c3bdad7719b534e7db1cb93c.jpg\" /><p>A week after releasing a teaser for a new horror game seemingly called <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/emio-nintendo-switch-horror-trailer-teaser-youtube-1851584450\">Emio</a>, Nintendo has pulled back the curtain on the mysterious project with a <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://x.com/nintendoamerica/status/1813560122549137533\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">full reveal</a>. Turns out, it isn\u2019t exactly what the creepy <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VbhwwG-QvGQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">first trailer</a> made it out to be, and is instead a new entry in the long-dormant <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/these-famicom-detectiv", "id": 881341, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/nintendo-who-is-emio-famicom-detective-club-horror-1851596350", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/14ed0ec3c3bdad7719b534e7db1cb93c.jpg", "title": "Nintendo Reveals Its Mysterious Horror Game And It's Not What Fans Expected", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T13:35:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b6a392f3f02e896f64f6936d3de38be4.jpg\" /><p>As No Man\u2019s Sky nears its eight anniversary, it\u2019s clear the open-world survival crafting sim isn\u2019t slowing down. <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/no-mans-sky-adrift-update-expedition-horror-abandoned-1851506331\">A cavalcade of free updates</a> continues to transform the game from what it once was at launch, and the latest of those is no different. Today, Hello Games revealed  Worlds Part 1, a complete overhaul of\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/no-man-sky-patch-5-0-free-helldivers-mechs-1851596276\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 880907, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/no-man-sky-patch-5-0-free-helldivers-mechs-1851596276", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b6a392f3f02e896f64f6936d3de38be4.jpg", "title": "No Man's Sky Is Getting A Complete Universal Refresh In One Of Its Biggest Updates Ever", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-07-17T12:00:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/60f85a944eb4d2ad67e7fedc118ae5dc.jpg\" /><p>The world has been plunged into darkness. The dead persist violently among the living. What remains of humanity following a cataclysm I helped trigger is now at each other\u2019s throats. I carry my share of the blame, but it\u2019s clear the gods must pay for what they\u2019ve done to us. There\u2019s a path to seeking justice, and it\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/flintlock-game-review-soulslike-ashen-difficult-1851595559\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 880480, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/flintlock-game-review-soulslike-ashen-difficult-1851595559", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/60f85a944eb4d2ad67e7fedc118ae5dc.jpg", "title": "Flintlock: The Siege Of Dawn: The Kotaku Review", "user": null, "vote": 0}]